parameters.name: Config
parameters.description: The configurations of the media fingerprint library. By default, this parameter is left empty. You can customize the configurations based on your business requirements. The value must be a string in the JSON format.

parameters.name: Description
parameters.description: The description of the media fingerprint library.

parameters.name: ModelId
parameters.description: The model ID of the media fingerprint library. To create a text fingerprint library, set the parameter to **11**. To create a video fingerprint library, set the parameter to **12**. To create an audio fingerprint library, set the parameter to **13**. To create an image fingerprint library, set the parameter to **14**.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the media fingerprint library.
